Description:
THE PRIDE OF KEILOR
Superbly positioned just walking distance from Calder Rise Neighborhood Park, this inviting family home is defined by light-filled living spaces, zoned entertaining areas and a flexible floor plan over two levels.
Formal living and dining rooms open via French doors to the front entry, a well-planned central kitchen with plenty of storage and dishwasher sits adjacent to a bright dining room with servery.
Downstairs features three bedrooms, BIRs, central bathroom with separate bath, shower and vanity.
The second level comprises master bedroom with BIRs, separate bathroom facilities and large rumpus room with built in bar, balcony and entertaining areas.
Additional appointments include polished floor boards, gas wall heater, split system air conditioning, ceiling fans, 1000 litre water tank, landscaped gardens boasting paved low maintenance BBQ area, drive through garage and workshop.
Peacefully positioned in quiet court location, enviably close to parklands, St Augustine's Primary School, Overnewton, Keilor Village Township and easy freeway access.
A beautiful outdoor garden oasis is what you will find stepping into this picturesque four bedroom double story brick residence which represents the epitome of family living with an emphasis on quality and detail. Inspect today!
Maurice Moschini

Description:
listedAS A Wonderful Lifestyle Awaits
Nestled in a quiet court right next to Keilor Downs Recreation Reserve is this wonderful and inspired family lifestyle home. Behind a picturesque tree-lined façade is a great sized family home which includes 3 bedrooms with built-in robes, 2 large bathrooms, and a large formal lounge with gas heater and air conditioner.
The kitchen has been updated with plenty of cupboard space and flows through to the rumpus room which features floor to ceiling height windows and views of the backyard and the solar heated pool.
Perfect for a family with kids, the pool will be the envy of all their friends. A steel pool gate safely blocks off the pool from the large backyard and the built-in bbq with gas connection is a bonus.
Other features include evaporative cooling, ceiling fans, new blinds in the rumpus, garage with heaps of storage, and a large pergola which is being used as a billiards area.
Walking distance to schools, parks, while also being close enough to Keilor Central and St Albans Leisure Centre.
Our signs are everywhere... winningAS
Note: Every care has been taken to verify the accuracy of the details in this advertisement, however, we cannot guarantee its correctness. Prospective purchasers are requested to take such action as is necessary, to satisfy themselves of any pertinent matters.

Description:
MOVE IN & ENJOY!
Please book now.for.your one.on.one.appointment
Beautifully presented and elegantly maintained throughout by the same family since new. With stunning features and larger than normal living, this elevated brick residence will impress any astute buyers and also provides the potential to enhance even further.
The home comprises of:
• Three carpeted bedrooms with 2 bedrooms complete with BIRs
• Stunning central bathroom and separate toilet
• Spacious light filled formal lounge
• Formal dining / 4th bedroom /study
• Kitchen finishes with quality appliances adjoining dining area,
• Outdoor sunroom provides a perfect place to relax.
• Brick garage and carport
More Key Features:
• Sitting on approximate 534m² of land
• Roller Shutters throughout
• Wooden Laminate flooring
• High Ceilings, 2.7m
• A long drive-way provides space for the arrival of guests,
Bonus: Garage & 2nd toilet outside with Gas, Electric and Water connections, potential for a self-contained unit
Set in a prime pocket of Kings Park, within walking distance to parks, primary & secondary schools and public transport, only a short drive to Caroline Springs, Watergardens Shopping Centre and Keilor Downs Plaza. This fantastic family home ticks all the right boxes!

Description:
DOUBLE INCOME - TWO FOR THE PRICE OF ONE
Opportunity to secure this three bedroom plus two bedroom residence, leased for $600 per week in total. Features include renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, modern bathroom, built in wall unit, split system air conditioner, Rinnai gas heaters, large rear garden with shade sail and double garage. Gas and electricity separately metered and second water meter. Situated moments from St Albans Shopping Centre, new train station complex, Victoria University and schools. Land 542m2 corner configuration with side access from common driveway will enhance redevelopment potential, subject to planning approval.

Description:
Magnificent Modern Renovation with a Family Focus
Instruction is that the property is to be sold by way of online Auction- Friday 2nd October at 5pm- unless negotiated and sold prior.
Beautifully renovated, this modern family home will impress from beginning to end.
Set on a spacious suburban block, the property begins with an open front yard and sun-drenched porch, before you enter onto warming hardwood floors which flow throughout the home.
The semi-formal lounge is flooded with natural light and with a ceiling fan, split system heating/cooling for comfort, before making your way into an open dining room and kitchen precinct.
The kitchen offers stone benches, stainless steel appliances including a built-in gas cooktop, under bench oven (900mm) and range hood. It also has an integrated Asko dishwasher and an island bench to finish off the kitchen experience.
Bedroom accommodation is housed off the hallway where all bedrooms have robes and ceiling fans for comfort, as well as proximity to the bathroom with floor-to-ceiling tiles, corner shower, vanity, separate inset bath and heat light.
A separate laundry provides direct access to a sensational outdoor area, highlighted by a brilliant covered entertaining deck which overlooks plenty of private backyard for the kids and pets to explore.
A double garage/workshop, secure off-street parking options, vegetable patches and gas ducted heating further contributes to an incredible opportunity in a picture perfect location.
Positioned close to all the area has to offer including shopping, schools, cafes and restaurants, with easy access to public transport, major roads, Citylink and Melbourne's Tullamarine Airport, this is a lifestyle choice for the better.
